00:00:13.230 --> 00:00:15.010 align:middle line:90%
But is it?

00:00:15.010 --> 00:00:18.150 align:middle line:84%
In this episode, we explore
the fullness of space

00:00:18.150 --> 00:00:21.030 align:middle line:84%
and what it means to our
understanding of physics

00:00:21.030 --> 00:00:22.532 align:middle line:90%
