You will never
arrive at the end.

00:13:06.960 --> 00:13:12.690 align:middle line:84%
If there is energy there, then
it has an infinite potential.

00:13:12.690 --> 00:13:18.090 align:middle line:84%
Clearly, this could
be a source of energy

00:13:18.090 --> 00:13:23.640 align:middle line:84%
with infinite potential for
humanity, a source of energy

00:13:23.640 --> 00:13:27.840 align:middle line:84%
that would give us something
that could be thought

00:13:27.840 --> 00:13:30.450 align:middle line:90%
of as gravity control.

00:13:30.450 --> 00:13:35.100 align:middle line:84%
There's all kinds of
application in realizing

00:13:35.100 --> 00:13:40.260 align:middle line:84%
that we are all bathing
in this infinite,

00:13:40.260 --> 00:13:43.770 align:middle line:84%
or very close to
infinite, level of energy

00:13:43.770 --> 00:13:45.590 align:middle line:90%
that we call the vacuum.

00:13:45.590 --> 00:13:51.270 align:middle line:84%
We're discovering that this
vacuum energy is everywhere,

00:13:51.270 --> 00:13:53.850 align:middle line:84%
and that it's
producing everything.

00:13:53.850 --> 00:13:58.080 align:middle line:84%
And so we are starting
to think maybe

00:13:58.080 --> 00:14:01.440 align:middle line:90%
we can become vacuum engineers.

00:14:01.440 --> 00:14:04.800 align:middle line:84%
We can engineer
the vacuum together

00:14:04.800 --> 00:14:09.570 align:middle line:84%
to do a little bit of
what we want it to do.

00:14:09.570 --> 00:14:12.180 align:middle line:84%
